    website: "",
    scholar: "",
    bio: "Shreya is a PhD candidate at the Wee Kim Wee School of Communication and Information. Her research centers on human-AI interaction and the psychological effects of information communication technologies. Currently, she is examining the effects of interacting with AI that attempts to explain how and why it made a decision or action (explainable AI or XAI), and how this impacts the interaction experience."
  },
  {
    id: "li-xie",
    name: "Li Xie",
    title: "Lab Member",
